'''线粒体拟核'''（{{lang-en|mitochondrial nucleoid}}）是一种存在于[[线粒体|线粒体]]内类似[[原核细胞|原核细胞]]的[[拟核|拟核]]的结构，是由[[线粒体DNA|线粒体DNA]]（mtDNA）和多种[[蛋白质|蛋白质]]组成的[[核蛋白|核蛋白]][[复合物|复合物]]。线粒体拟核一般呈颗粒状分布于[[线粒体基质|线粒体基质]]的特定位置，并经某些蛋白质锚定在[[线粒体内膜|线粒体内膜]]内侧表面上。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Kucej M, Butow RA
 | title = Evolutionary tinkering with mitochondrial nucleoids
 | journal = Trends in Cell Biology
 | volume = 17
 | issue = 12
 | pages = 586-592
 | pmid = 17981466
 | doi = 10.1016/j.tcb.2007.08.007
 | url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=MImg&_imagekey=B6TCX-4R2GX01-1-1&_cdi=5182&_user=2324792&_pii=S0962892407002425&_origin=&_coverDate=12%2F31%2F2007&_sk=999829987&view=c&wchp=dGLzVlb-zSkzk&md5=b1282dbf49c76b38132575e1afe13bc8&ie=/sdarticle.pdf
 | language = en |date=Dec 2007}}</ref>线粒体拟核能直接或间接地与[[驱动蛋白|驱动蛋白]]进行[[相互作用|相互作用]]，在线粒体分裂中作为mtDNA分离的基本单位。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Chen XJ, Butow RA
 | title = The organization and inheritance of the mitochondrial genome
 | journal = Nature Reviews Genetics
 | volume = 6
 | issue = 11
 | pages = 815-825
 | pmid = 16304597
 | doi = 10.1038/nrg1708
 | url = http://www.nature.com/nrg/journal/v6/n11/abs/nrg1708.html
 | language = en |date=Nov 2005}}</ref>
目前已在多种[[真菌|真菌]]、[[植物|植物]]和[[哺乳动物|哺乳动物]]的线粒体中发现了拟核，说明该结构可能是[[真核细胞|真核细胞]]内mtDNA的普遍存在形式。

线粒体拟核的[[密度|密度]]远高于[[细胞分裂#分裂间期|间期]]的[[细胞核|细胞核]]，甚至高于[[细胞分裂|细胞分裂]][[细胞分裂#中期(metaphase)|中期]]的[[染色体|染色体]]。这说明mtDNA必须进行压缩折叠才能装配成紧凑的拟核。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = J F Diffley, B Stillman 
 | title = A close relative of the nuclear, chromosomal high-mobility group protein HMG1 in yeast mitochondria
 | journal = Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America 
 | volume = 88
 | issue = 17
 | pages = 7864-7868
 | pmid = 1881919
 | doi = 
 | url = http://www.pnas.org/content/88/17/7864.full.pdf
 | language = en |date=Sep 1, 1991}}</ref>以[[酵母菌|酵母菌]]为例，根据生理状态的不同，单个酵母菌中可含有10-40个线粒体拟核，平均每个拟核中则可含有1-2个mtDNA[[分子|分子]]。[[酿酒酵母|酿酒酵母]]线粒体拟核的直径约为400[[纳米|nm]]，远小于松弛状态下长约25[[微米|μm]]（80k[[碱基对|b]]）的mtDNA。酿酒酵母中执行装配拟核功能的是线粒体[[DNA结合蛋白|DNA结合蛋白]]Abf2（ARS-binding factor 2），该蛋白能将mtDNA进行压缩而不影响mtDNA[[基因|基因]]的[[转录|转录]]。哺乳动物线粒体拟核的形态和分布与酿酒酵母中的相似：在人的[[ECV304细胞|ECV304细胞]]中，mtDNA组成约475个拟核，不连续地分布于线粒体中, 每个拟核含6-10个mtDNA。

== 历史 ==
线粒体拟核是在20世纪70年代被发现的。1974年研究人员用[[氨银染色法|氨银染色法]]在[[多头绒泡菌|多头绒泡菌]]（''Physarum polycephalum''）线粒体中观察了这种颗粒结构。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = T. Kuroiwa and M. Hizume
 | title = Mitochondrial nucleoid staining with ammoniacal silver
 | journal = 
 | volume = 87
 | issue = 2
 | pages = 406-409
 | pmid = 4137845
 | doi = 10.1016/0014-4827(74)90504-7
 | url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0014482774905047
 | language = en |date=Aug 1974}}</ref>随后，在1976年人们成功将其从线粒体中分离出来，并利用[[SDS-聚丙烯酰胺凝胶电泳|SDS-聚丙烯酰胺凝胶电泳]]证实线粒体拟核中含有蛋白质。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = T. Kuroiwa, S. Kawano and M. Hizume
 | title = A method of isolation of mitochondrial nucleoid of Physarum polycephalum and evidence for the presence of a basic protein
 | journal = Experimental Cell Research
 | volume = 97
 | issue = 2
 | pages = 435-440
 | pmid = 942924
 | doi = 10.1016/0014-4827(76)90638-8
 | url = http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/0014482776906388
 | language = en |date=Feb 1976}}</ref>1984年，研究人员发现线粒体拟核的形态在细胞的不同生理状态、[[细胞周期|细胞周期]]不同时期中组成、形态都不同。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Miyakawa I, Aoi H, Sando N, Kuroiwa T
 | title = Fluorescence microscopic studies of mitochondrial nucleoids during meiosis and sporulation in the yeast, Saccharomyces cerevisiae
