 | language = en |date=Mar 1984}}</ref>进入21世纪后，线粒体拟核的组织结构和[[遗传|遗传]]模式已被较系统地阐明。<ref>{{cite journal
 | author = Chen XJ, Wang X, Kaufman BA, Butow RA
 | title = Aconitase couples metabolic regulation to mitochondrial DNA maintenance
